OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,FThe number of pets being abandoned in
OL,7,F2023 has risen by a third, figures
OL,8,Freleased by the RSPCA have revealed.
OL,10,FAnimals being abandoned in Greater
OL,11,FManchester rose to 1,250 from 942 in
OL,12,F2021 when the cost of living crisis
OL,13,Fbegan.
OL,15,FAcross England and Wales the number of
OL,16,Fanimals abandoned during the winter
OL,17,Fperiod has increased by 51% in just
OL,18,Fthree years, the charity said.
