OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,FThe RSPCA has released the new
OL,7,Fstartling statistics to highlight the
OL,8,Fbattle frontline rescuers face ahead
OL,9,Fof what is expected to be another
OL,10,Fbleak winter for thousands of animals
OL,11,Fas part of its Join The Christmas
OL,12,FRescue campaign.
OL,14,FIt received 3,071 animal abandonment
OL,15,Freports during the winter period
OL,16,F(November to January 2021).
OL,18,FLast winter, November 2023 to January
OL,19,F2024, it rose to 4,630 pets who were
OL,20,Freported to have been left to fend for
OL,21,Fthemselves - a 51% increase.
