OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,FIn total 20,999 abandonment reports
OL,7,Fwere made to the charity's emergency
OL,8,Fline in 2023 and according to latest
OL,9,F2024 figures (available up until the
OL,10,Fend of October) 19,067 have been
OL,11,Freported this year - which, the
OL,12,Fcharity says, if the trend continues,
OL,13,Fwill be almost 23,000 reports.
OL,15,FBefore the cost of living crisis the
OL,16,Fnumber of reported abandonments during
OL,17,F2020 stood at 16,118 reports - showing
OL,18,Fa 30% rise in calls in just three
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
