OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,FThe RSPCA believes the surge in pet
OL,7,Fownership during the Covid-19 lockdown
OL,8,Fand the increasing financial hardships
OL,9,Fdue to soaring living costs have led
OL,10,Fto the increase in people dumping
OL,11,Ftheir pets.
OL,13,FAnd sadly now, during the winter
OL,14,Fmonths, the RSPCA expects the crisis
OL,15,Fto worsen as more people struggle with
OL,16,Fthe increase in expenditure around
OL,17,FChristmas time with presents to buy
OL,18,Fand extra food shopping - coupled with
OL,19,Fan increase in energy bills.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
