OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,FRSPCA Chief Inspector Ian Briggs said:
OL,7,F"We are seeing a shocking rise in the
OL,8,Fnumber of calls reporting pet
OL,9,Fabandonment to our emergency line
OL,10,Fduring winter with an eye-watering 51%
OL,11,Frise in three years.
OL,13,FSadly we expect the trend will
OL,14,Fcontinue as more pet owners face
OL,15,Ffinancial hardship at this time of
OL,16,Fyear more than any other.
