OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,F"Our rescuers are regularly coming
OL,7,Facross dogs in poor health, collapsed
OL,8,Fand left in isolated spots to suffer a
OL,9,Flingering death; sick kittens
OL,10,Fdiscarded in cardboard boxes who are
OL,11,Flucky to be found alive; or pet
OL,12,Frabbits dumped in the wild with little
OL,13,Fchance of survival against predators.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
