OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,F"With the cost of living crisis we are
OL,7,Falso seeing people having to move out
OL,8,Fof properties due to financial
OL,9,Fpressures, and we are increasingly
OL,10,Fcoming across pets who have been left
OL,11,Flocked in homes alone after their
OL,12,Fowners have moved out - like Jack and
OL,13,FPoppy pictured who were left to starve
OL,14,Fon a filthy mattress but were rescued
OL,15,Fby the RSPCA and have since been
OL,16,Frehomed.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
