OL,3,CNumber of animals abandoned rises
OL,4,Cdramatically
OL,6,F"Heartbreakingly, we are seeing many
OL,7,Fpets left in their own filth - with no
OL,8,Ffood or water, no-one to care for them
OL,9,Fand no idea if anyone will come to
OL,10,Fhelp them.
OL,12,F"Thanks to the public supporting us we
OL,13,Fare able to rescue many animals,
OL,14,Frehabilitate them and find them new
OL,15,Fhomes - but to continue this life-
OL,16,Fsaving work we need your help."
OL,18,FTo help the RSPCA rescue more animals
OL,19,Fvisit rspca.org.uk/winterappeal
